SAML Workflow
==============
1.SP initiated authentication.
2.IDP imnitiated authentication.

WorkFlow
=========

SP Initiated authentication.
==============================
1.user try to access the app(Service provider)
2.The application detects the domain and generate a saml request to browser
3.Browser forward the saml request to IDP
4.IDP provides the login screen
5.User provide credential and request authentication
6.IDP authenticate and forward saml response.
7.Browser forward the saml response to application
8.Application forward the saml assertion to Assertion consumer service(ACS)
9.ACS validates the assetion and inform application
10.Application provide the protective resource to the browser.

IDP:Okta,Auth0

Current version of saml is 2.0
===============================

Service provider functionality 
1.Generate saml request
2.Validate saml response and based on validation allow/deny access to protected resource.





          

